  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>A spirit of battle dwells within your armaments. Select one weapon or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.FNDq4NFSN0g2HKWO]{Handwraps of Mighty Blows} when you make your daily preparations. In your hands, the item gains the effect of a property rune.</p><hr /><p>From <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.classfeatures.Item.EtltLdiy9kNfHU0c]{Blessed Armament}</em></p><p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.hnbbqvzYDyhDiJnf]{Bane}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.LwQb7ryTC8FlOXgX]{Vitalizing}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.JQdwHECogcTzdd8R]{Ghost Touch}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.P6v2AtJw7AUwaDzf]{Fearsome}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.qlunQzfnzPQpMG6U]{Returning}, or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.roeYtwlIe65BPMJ1]{Shifting}</p><hr /><p>From <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.h5ksUZlrVGBjq6p4]{Radiant Armament}</em>:</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.6llILJtsTPgtYXgx]{Astral}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.LbdnZFlyLFdAE617]{Brilliant}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.DH0kB9Wbr5pDeunX]{Holy}, or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.gmMrJREf4JSHd2dZ]{Unholy}</p><hr /><p>From <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.jYEMVfrXJLpXS6aC]{Armament Paragon}</em>:</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.DCPsilr8wbPXxTUv]{Animated}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.oVrVzML63VFvVfKk]{Vitalizing (Greater)}, or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.hg3IogR8ue2IWwgS]{Keen}</p>"
    },
